        "solution": "one GameLevel data model for 2D, board, and 3D",
        "proof": "the three canonical game captures"
      },
      {
        "problem": "large-world memory",
        "solution": "chunk and region streaming around the camera",
        "proof": "StreamingTerrain and RegionProvider described in the article"
      }
    ]
